commit.title: Ensuring a warning for local declaration invisible in current goal.
commit.message:
Ensuring a warning for local declaration invisible in current goal.

In the case of a variable declared while in a goal which itself is in
a section, there used to be a message. We move it to a warning.

In the case of a local definition built interactively while in an
other goal which itself is in a section, there used to be no
message at all. We add a warning.
